OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally has been
OL,8,Fspeaking to mothers Emma Murphy and
OL,9,FJanet Williams who campaign for
OL,10,Ffamilies affected by Sodium Valproate.
OL,12,FTwo mothers campaigning for
OL,13,Fcompensation for victims of a drug
OL,14,Fthat caused up to 20,000 children to
OL,15,Fbe born with birth defects say they
OL,16,Fare being "totally ignored" by the new
OL,17,FLabour government.
