OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FBut since Labour came into power Emma
OL,7,Fand Janet say they have had no
OL,8,Fcommunication from the new government,
OL,9,Fdespite writing several letters to the
OL,10,FHealth Secretary.
OL,12,FEmma, from Greater Manchester, and
OL,13,FJanet, from Lancashire, delivered
OL,14,Fanother letter to Downing Street on
OL,15,FWednesday, 6 November, urging the
OL,16,FPrime Minister to honour the report's
OL,17,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
