OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,F"The families that we represent feel
OL,7,Fignored by this government", Emma
OL,8,Fsaid. "We've written to the Health
OL,9,FSecretary four times. We've written to
OL,10,Fthe Treasury two times and we're not
OL,11,Fhearing anything back."
OL,13,FJanet added: "We felt we were at the
OL,14,Fcusp of a victory but since Labour has
OL,15,Fcome in we do feel ignored, just like
OL,16,Fthe postmasters. This is just as
OL,17,Fimportant."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
