OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare said it is "committed to
OL,8,Fproviding an update to the Patient
OL,9,FSafety Commissioner at the earliest
OL,10,Fopportunity."
OL,12,FWhat is Sodium Valproate?
OL,14,FSodium valproate is an effective drug
OL,15,Fused to treat epilepsy, which was
OL,16,Flicensed in 1973 - but as early as the
OL,17,F1980s reports of babies born with
OL,18,Fdeformities began to surface.
