OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FAfter decades of parents and medical
OL,7,Fpractitioners raising safety concerns,
OL,8,Fa 2020 review, called the Cumberlege
OL,9,FReport, concluded that thousands of
OL,10,Fmothers and babies had been exposed to
OL,11,F"avoidable harm".
OL,13,FThe Patient Safety Commissioner
OL,14,Frecommended the Government set up
OL,15,Finterim payments and a full
OL,16,Fcompensation scheme in February 2024 -
OL,17,Fbut no action has been taken.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
