OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FAll five of Emma's children have Fetal
OL,7,Fvalproate spectrum disorder (FVSD) and
OL,8,Faffected in various ways, with
OL,9,Fdiagnoses of cerebral palsy,
OL,10,Fincontinence, deafness, speech and
OL,11,Flanguage delay, valgus foot, and
OL,12,Fsensory processing disorder.
OL,14,FJanet was prescribed the drug while
OL,15,Fpregnant with her two sons in 1989 and
OL,16,F1991 - both have FVSD and are unlikely
OL,17,Fto be able to live independently.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
