OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,FJanet and Emma run INFACT (Independent
OL,7,FFetal Anti Convulsant Trust), a
OL,8,Fcampaign group to raise awareness and
OL,9,Furge government action on all of the
OL,10,Frecommendations set out in the
OL,11,FCumberlege Report, including
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,F"A lot of these families are
OL,15,Fstruggling financially", Janet added.
OL,16,F"They have done for a quite a long
OL,17,Fwhile, especially now the benefits
OL,18,Fsystem has changed and they've all
OL,19,Fbeen moved over onto Universal Credit
OL,20,Fas well.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
