OL,3,CFamilies affected by birth defect drug
OL,4,C'totally ignored' by government
OL,6,F"There are some fathers who cannot
OL,7,Fwork because they're caring for their
OL,8,Fepileptic wife and their disabled
OL,9,Fchild. To get that interim payment in
OL,10,Fplace would make a huge difference to
OL,11,Fthese families."
OL,13,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "Our sympathies are
OL,15,Fwith those affected by sodium
OL,16,Fvalproate and vaginal mesh and this
OL,17,Fgovernment is fully focused on how
OL,18,Fbest to support patients and prevent
OL,19,Ffuture harm.
